{"tid":1460674,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[緊急呼籲]未有百份百FC前，唔好再擺上網批鬥","createTime":"2019-08-13T04:17:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T17:56:28.000Z","uid":129622,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"ca86da99dbfe1e803219208d9aa172d2d547eca2","tid":1460674,"uid":129622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T04:17:58.000Z","msg":"之前致富炒過車 話會炒罷工員工<br />\n最後原來連董事都一齊罷工<br />\n仲真人上埋連登恥笑你<br />\n<br />\n然後Facebook有人寫自己係Coffee Art打工<br />\n講完藍屍野就屈哂落間Cafe<br />\n結果人地根本無呢個員工<br />\n老闆仲要自己人<br />\n<br />\n到今次搵仔Group連地址都起錯 仲要質問自己手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我認同批鬥撚屌係必需 但真係要百份百FC過先 傷到自己人係最唔可以接受既事<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Gnqm1tt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGnqm1tt.png&h=de89c508&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"196b66c4018aa2bdba03a976c2f8988925dba32e","tid":1460674,"uid":215612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T04:19:55.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"f8c83f5c8518638ca06a4398fd5733c2d9f93a74","tid":1460674,"uid":129622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"196b66c4018aa2bdba03a976c2f8988925dba32e","tid":1460674,"uid":215612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T04:19:55.000Z","msg":"幫推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T04:21:21.000Z","msg":"813機場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc9d16c90fcc1688f3c76b8844f32c3b5d2666ae","tid":1460674,"uid":147721,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T04:21:28.000Z","msg":"痴線 尋晚有幾個人都認為放錯料無問題事後道歉咪得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03e35ca827ea513e13d066d22a4eda5b3457af2f","tid":1460674,"uid":129622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T04:21:53.000Z","msg":"記住 撚屌一定要批鬥<br />\n但要做足功課先擺上來啊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12097664b10207228e74d3155f64ff8c5a26789c","tid":1460674,"uid":98431,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T04:22:35.000Z","msg":"因為有鬼放流料 想轉移視線<br />\n<br />\n順便借力打力 製造假煙幕令人內鬥<br />\n<br />\n切中計 柒左就認"},{"pid":"28e29783e7d0e7051b30e4a4a6d634f1e21561fa","tid":1460674,"uid":124146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T04:22:37.000Z","msg":"琴日好多被盜用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82b95cd7a328b2b79c593d17415df4a3d0e6f1b3","tid":1460674,"uid":288580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T04:22:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3df1e608da5d765c23f00a37efef367dc33b8ed6","tid":1460674,"uid":67553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T04:22:44.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"1c2a828b02ba567fe99d2fa434eb5fb0ed43d3d4","tid":1460674,"uid":33875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T04:23:16.000Z","msg":"最大鑊係試過將義士電話放咗上嚟話係黑警電話 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d3ba60c286cdc5e0a718dcff6e42ab45bffdfb5","tid":1460674,"uid":129622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T04:27:00.000Z","msg":"813機場"},{"pid":"b3002f68a36f490508271a45b5be828719c2e29e","tid":1460674,"uid":111651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T04:33:37.000Z","msg":"-------------------------------------------------------<br />\n唔好意思阻阻大家<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TanfJ05.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTanfJ05.png&h=d6671254&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"58242f275e8d03ab6ce379ddba3e5a5e1ce4088e","tid":1460674,"uid":129622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T05:11:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"610a8a438df0d897a504fe23a64ed2bc437e2086","tid":1460674,"uid":254361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T05:12:43.000Z","msg":"借位講幾句野<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我求下各位巴打絲打<br />\n用腦諗下，要自主思考呀<br />\n留又好，唔留又好請交給在場人士去決定<br />\n同埋連登被嚴重滲透之下<br />\n各種謠言滿天飛，更加要冷靜思考<br />\n要多方面去證實嗰篇文是否真實<br />\n再去諗下佢發呢個信息佢個目的係乜嘢<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n和理非非會驚好多野係正常<br />\n（唔驚又有行動力做左勇武）<br />\n但係但係呢到我有幾句野想講<br />\n<br />\n直面面對「恐怖」，知道它的「傷害」<br />\n理解會造成的「後果」，站起來、面對它<br />\n這才是「勇氣」，這才是「抗爭」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔知大家有沒有看過周星馳的電影「少林足球」<br />\n當然還有其他優秀的電影，如「讓子彈飛一會」「V怪客」等等<br />\n<br />\n「少林足球」里的大反派說了這麼幾句<br />\n<br />\n強雄：「我是打人,怎麼樣? 我要把你全隊的人打得像你一樣殘廢、殘廢、殘廢... 跟我鬥?」<br />\n強雄：「還有球證、旁證加上主辦、協辦所有的單位，全部都是我的人，怎麼和我鬥?」<br />\n<br />\n係呀點鬥呀，只剩下咩可以去鬥呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以用你的力量與聲音，用你的方法去「抗爭」<br />\n力量聲音沒分大細，沒分方法嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n（細音說，方法有分成本效益的）<br />\n加油呀，香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後再講返幾句名言<br />\n曼德拉語錄:<br />\n如果天空是黑暗的，那就摸黑生存;<br />\n如果發出聲音是危險的，那就保持沉默;<br />\n如果自覺無力發光，那就蜷伏於牆角。<br />\n但是，不要習慣了黑暗就為黑暗辯護;<br />\n也不要為自己的苟且而得意;<br />\n不要嘲諷那些比自己更勇敢的人。<br />\n我們可以卑微如塵土，但不可扭曲如蛆蟲。<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;曼德拉《漫漫人生路》"},{"pid":"84a28b02dd6aabb0b5f2a5782873ab84a4f1806f","tid":1460674,"uid":49753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T05:13:49.000Z","msg":"尋日有哂共識，有狗叫人留機場就係鬼！<br />\n<br />\n[連登捉鬼] 同我BLOCK哂叫人留機場嘅人!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1455659\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1455659</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n所有叫人留機場嘅都係鬼<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1455203\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1455203</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n跪求係機場既手足快d走 唔好理d唔肯走既鬼<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1455160\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1455160</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n［置頂］ 機場即撒 十萬火急 唔好俾鬼搞事<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1455040\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1455040</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n你話我係鬼我都要照講，機場手足快d走，目的已達！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1454974\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1454974</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"eb5052f4366f11413b903d542b1dea4b48c8e186","tid":1460674,"uid":173814,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"12097664b10207228e74d3155f64ff8c5a26789c","tid":1460674,"uid":98431,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T04:22:35.000Z","msg":"因為有鬼放流料 想轉移視線<br />\n<br />\n順便借力打力 製造假煙幕令人內鬥<br />\n<br />\n切中計 柒左就認"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T05:18:00.000Z","msg":"根本有d係私怨撚<br />\n上次海港城shopping單野又係咁，無啦啦要質海港城<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲要質一個根本無人識既集團<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c74758ca7090647d479949a7552bbb92630c01b","tid":1460674,"uid":264529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T05:19:51.000Z","msg":"."},{"pid":"cb54d2c93f1816d6c5d8acb03688d69503a42bcf","tid":1460674,"uid":229886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T05:23:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f32a5db37e50b22a3c7b2d61847d6f108e510c1e","tid":1460674,"uid":56107,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T05:26:12.000Z","msg":"一手報料唔可能百份百FC<br />\n最多有個方向俾你睇下有幾似"},{"pid":"1da734f8da3a80da686b037a02525ce2a9e5b509","tid":1460674,"uid":151498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T05:27:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0fe168da1d723fda1117124bd004e032927c